HEADWORD: mail call
<hw>mail call</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A call of the names of those
persons receiving mail for the purpose of transmitting mail to them; --
a technique used in the military services to deliver mail to enlisted
personnel.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

